  <div class="mt-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-5 mb-10 text-justify">
    Experienced in definition and management of data-related products for
    organisations in telecoms, retail and digital tech. My ambition is to work
    with the best data product managers and engineers in the field to define and
    engineer scalable data platforms for the future. Those that scale not just
    for volume but for use cases from enterprise analytics to machine learning.
    So that we can be ready for when the next business opportunity arises.
