    <TimeLineElement
      title="Data Product Manager"
      subtitle="April 2014 - June 2023 | Sony Interactive Entertainment (PlayStation), London, UK"
    >
      (Aug 2018 - June 2023)
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
        Staff Product Manager, ensuring that PlayStation's commercial business
        is supported with reusable, robust and scalable data products, both
        today and in the long term.
      </ul>
      (Nov 2016 - Jul 2018)
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
        Product Owner for PlayStation Europe's core business performance
        reporting.<br />Delivery of curated dashboards and reports to
        PlayStation Europe executive management.
      </ul>
      (Apr 2014 - Oct 2016)
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
