          Implementation of imbalanced classification techniques to capture
          high-value but infrequent trading opportunities involving: Custom loss
          functions, smote, custom feature engineering, grid search, scaling &
          transforming, custom metrics.
        </li><li>
          Training, validation and testing of models evaluated via statistical
          bootstrap techniques.
        </li><li>Codebase & Tools: Python, Tensorflow, neptune.ai.</li>
      </ul>
